data.description: Brand new flooring throughout, brand new paint throughout.  The views are incredible.  See all the way to Flagstaff and the red rock cliffs near Sedona.  Surrounded by tall pines on private road.  Room for an RV parking spot at south end of property.  Primary and guest room on top floor.  In-Law suite on ground floor (walk out basement)  Extra deep garage for work shop space.  Covered deck on 2 sides. Terrific opportunity for Air B&B with tremendous views.  NO HOA  Countertops were removed for drywall work and due to age, not replaced.  Price reduced accordingly.
